# LogSentryWave - Pattern-Aware Log Analyzer

LogSentryWave surfaces recurring log patterns and abnormal events by analyzing time and message repetition.

## Features
- Frequency and keyword scan  
- Detects time-based bursts  
- CLI-friendly  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_LogSentryWave.git
cd 24_LogSentryWave
python analyze.py
